'''Bluefruit Kintle''' was a [[Tea/Legends|tea]] available from the kitchen stores aboard the [[DS-1 Orbital Battle Station/Legends|first Death Star]]. It was also one of several drinks served at the [[Hard Heart Cantina/Legends|Hard Heart Cantina]].<ref name="Death Star novel">[[Death Star (novel)|''Death Star'']]</ref>

